<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Words Ending With -ISM — Scrabble Suffix Scoring Guide</h1>
<p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6">Published June 15, 2026 · 5 min read</p>

<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">The -ISM suffix creates nouns that represent beliefs, systems, and practices — optimism, criticism, mysticism. With M worth 3 points and 300+ valid words, -ISM is a reliable path to bingo plays. Better yet, every -ISM word has a matching -IST form, so learning one pattern teaches you two.</p>

<p>This dual learning approach makes -ISM one of the most efficient suffixes to study for competitive Scrabble improvement.</p>

<h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">Why -ISM Matters in Scrabble</h2>

<div class="not-prose my-6 p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10">
  <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-6 text-center">
    <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">5 pts</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">I(1)+S(1)+M(3) base</p></div>
    <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">300+</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Valid -ISM words</p></div>
    <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">5–12</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Letter length range</p></div>
  </div>
</div>

<p>The M tile is worth 3 points and moderately scarce (only 2 in the bag). -ISM words tend to be 7+ letters, making them natural bingo candidates. The suffix pairs beautifully with high-value roots: MYSTIC+ISM, WITTIC+ISM, CRITIC+ISM all contain C(3) or Y(4) for extra scoring power.</p>

<p>Because M is scarce, saving it for an -ISM bingo rather than using it in a low-scoring midgame play can be the difference between winning and losing.</p>

<h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">Top Scoring -ISM Words</h2>

<div class="overflow-x-auto not-prose my-6">
  <table class="w-full text-sm border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-sm">
    <thead class="bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800">
      <tr>
        <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Word</th>
        <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Points</th>
        <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Length</th>
        <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Notes</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-100 dark:divide-gray-800">
      <tr class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono font-bold">MYSTICISM</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-amber-600 font-bold">18</td><td class="px-4 py-3">9</td><td class="px-4 py-3">Y(4)+C(3)+M(3)</td></tr>
      <tr class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono font-bold">WITTICISM</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-amber-600 font-bold">16</td><td class="px-4 py-3">9</td><td class="px-4 py-3">W(4)+C(3) + bingo</td></tr>
      <tr class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono font-bold">CRITICISM</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-amber-600 font-bold">15</td><td class="px-4 py-3">9</td><td class="px-4 py-3">C(3)+C(3) + bingo</td></tr>
      <tr class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono font-bold">OPTIMISM</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-amber-600 font-bold">14</td><td class="px-4 py-3">8</td><td class="px-4 py-3">P(3)+M(3) + bingo</td></tr>
      <tr class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono font-bold">MECHANISM</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-amber-600 font-bold">18</td><td class="px-4 py-3">9</td><td class="px-4 py-3">M(3)+C(3)+H(4)</td></tr>
      <tr class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono font-bold">HEROISM</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-amber-600 font-bold">12</td><td class="px-4 py-3">7</td><td class="px-4 py-3">H(4) + bingo</td></tr>
